<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240527/1716808947057040875.png" title="1716808947057040875.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-27 192101.png" width="947" height="398" style="width: 947px; height: 398px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">为扎实推动党纪学习教育走深走实，进一步推进党纪学习教育读书班工作安排，经济管理学院教师党支部于5月16日在A10-407针对“六大纪律”开展党纪学习教育集中学习研讨。此次集中学习研讨由党总支书记蔡平带领学习，全体教师党员参加。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">内容概况本次集中学习研讨主要有以下两项内容：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">1、蔡平书记解读《中国共产党纪律处分条例》（以下简称《条例》）中“六大纪律”内容；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2、教师党员进行研讨。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240527/1716808993592078723.png" title="1716808993592078723.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-27 192112.png"/></span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">党总支书记蔡平解读《条例》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学习内容会议伊始，蔡平书记对《条例》中的“六大纪律”进行解读，“六大纪律”即政治纪律、组织纪律、廉洁纪律、群众纪律、工作纪律、生活纪律，是《条例》的重要部分，也是要重点学习把握、逐条对照检查的内容。他指出，全体教师党员要通过本次学习，深刻理解“六大纪律”内涵，对照“六大纪律”检视检查，查找自身问题，同时要将理论知识转化为工作实践，以身作则，严守纪律底线，把规矩当习惯，充分发挥党员干部的模范带头作用。</span></p></section></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240527/1716809073845022378.png" title="1716809073845022378.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-27 192122.png" width="909" height="546" style="width: 909px; height: 546px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">教师党员研讨</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">研讨心得随后，教师党员就本次集中学习进行研讨，分别从政治纪律、组织纪律、廉洁纪律、群众纪律、工作纪律、生活纪律进行了发言讨论。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1.刘孟</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">作为教师党员，我们要准确掌握“六大纪律”的主旨要义，做到学深悟透、融会贯通，真正使学习党纪的过程成为增强纪律意识、提升党性修养的过程。同时作为党员干部，必须要搞明白“六大纪律”是什么，弄明白能干什么，掌握住不能干什么，并结合自身工作岗位和个人情况，经常做到审视自身，并不断进行自我提高。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2.熊帆帆</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">通过对“六大纪律”的学习，我更加深刻地认识到遵守党的纪律的重要性。作为一名教师党员，我应当时刻保持清醒的头脑，坚定理想信念，严守党的政治纪律和政治规矩，同时要明晰党纪学习教育主线，聚焦修订后的《条例》，把学习教育与学校日常重点工作紧密结合起来，切实将纪律规矩转化为政治自觉、思想自觉、行动自觉，将学习成果转化为工作动力和实际行动，做到言行一致、表里如一。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">总结</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">本次集中学习研讨，旨在加强教师党员对“六大纪律”的学习和理解，进一步增强将党纪内化于心、外化于行的能力，确保在工作和生活中严格遵守党的纪律，用实际行动为学院的发展和学生的成长贡献自己的力量。</span></p>